ription\": \"Graph parsing, serialization, canonical byte generation, hashing, and RdfDelta transitions must be deterministic.\"\n-      }\n-    },\n-    {\n-      \"id\": \"req_r4_knowledge_hook\",\n-      \"type\": \"PRDRequirement\",\n-      \"attributes\": {\n-        \"title\": \"Knowledge Hook Runtime & Deterministic Scheduling\",\n-        \"description\": \"Turtle-based hook packs must load dynamically as graph laws and schedule deterministically.\"\n-      }\n-    },\n-    {\n-      \"id\": \"req_r5_ocel_prov\",\n-      \"type\": \"PRDRequirement\",\n-      \"attributes\": {\n-        \"title\": \"OCEL/PROV Evidence Projection & Replayable Receipts\",\n-        \"description\": \"Every graph transition must produce a replayable cryptographic receipt bundle and project PROV-O/OCEL.\"\n-      }\n-    },\n-    {\n-      \"id\": \"req_r6_compliance\",\n-      \"type\": \"PRDRequirement\",\n-      \"attributes\": {\n-        \"title\": \"Compliance Checks & Anti-Fake Gates\",\n-        \"description\": \"Must pass structural analyses checking for forbidden execution surfaces and zero placeholder/stub/mock/fake-success patterns.\"\n-      }\n-    },\n-    {\n-      \"id\": \"req_r7_ocel_self_audit\",\n-      \"type\": \"PRDRequirement\",\n-      \"attributes\": {\n-        \"title\": \"OCEL v2 Self-Audit Log Emission\",\n-        \"description\": \"Implement self-audit log generator emitting vision2030.self_audit.ocel.json.\"\n-      }\n-    },\n-    {\n-      \"id\": \"req_r8_coverage_matrix\",\n-      \"type\": \"PRDRequirement\",\n-      \"attributes\": {\n-        \"title\": \"Coverage Matrix & Verification Scripts\",\n-        \"description\": \"Implement coverage mapping in coverage.rs and verify via scripts.\"\n-      }\n-    },\n-    {\n-      \"id\": \"req_r9_proof_report\",\n-      \"type\": \"PRDRequirement\",\n-      \"attributes\": {\n-        \"description\": \"Establish Vision 2030 durable proof report.\",\n-        \"title\": \"Vision 2030 Durable Proof Report\"\n-      }\n-    },\n-    {\n-      \"id\": \"obj_cp_verify\",\n-      \"type\": \"GALLCheckpoint\",\n-      \"attributes\": {\n-        \"target_date\": \"2026-05-26Z\",\n-        \"milestone\": \"self_audit_verification\"\n-      }\n-    },\n-    {\n-      \"id\": \"obj_public_ontology\",\n-      \"type\": \"PublicOntology\",\n-      \"attributes\": {\n-        \"prefix\": \"ocel\",\n-        \"namespace\": \"http://www.ocel-standard.org/ns#\"\n-      }\n-    },\n-    {\n-      \"id\": \"obj_ontology_term_event\",\n-      \"type\": \"OntologyTerm\",\n-      \"attributes\": {\n-        \"name\": \"Event\",\n-        \"uri\": \"http://www.ocel-standard.org/ns#Event\"\n-      }\n-    },\n-    {\n-      \"id\": \"obj_source_file_self_audit\",\n-      \"type\": \"SourceFile\",\n-      \"attributes\": {\n-        \"path\": \"crates/ggen-graph/src/ocel/self_audit.rs\",\n-        \"language\": \"rust\"\n-      }\n-    },\n-    {\n-      \"id\": \"obj_test_file_self_audit\",\n-      \"type\": \"TestFile\",\n-      \"attributes\": {\n-        \"framework\": \"cargo test\",\n-        \"path\": \"crates/ggen-graph/tests/self_audit_tests.rs\"\n-      }\n-    },\n-    {\n-      \"id\": \"obj_example_file_self_audit\",\n-      \"type\": \"ExampleFile\",\n-      \"attributes\": {\n-        \"path\": \"crates/ggen-graph/examples/self_audit_demo.rs\",\n-        \"description\": \"Demonstrates generation and projection of self-audit log\"\n-      }\n-    },\n-    {\n-      \"id\": \"obj_fixture_file_self_audit\",\n-      \"type\": \"FixtureFile\",\n-      \"attributes\": {\n-        \"path\": \"crates/ggen-graph/tests/fixtures/self_audit_log.json\",\n-        \"format\": \"json\"\n-      }\n-    },\n-    {\n-      \"id\": \"obj_script_file_verify\",\n-      \"type\": \"ScriptFile\",\n-      \"attributes\": {\n-        \"interpreter\": \"bash\",\n-        \"path\": \"scripts/verify_self_audit_integrity.sh\"\n-      }\n-    },\n-    {\n-      \"id\": \"obj_command_test\